## The Thames Path Wellness Walk, 3 May has been cancelled
### It is with great sadness that we have to inform you that the Thames Path
Wellness Walk 2020 has been cancelled. We have a duty of care to all
participants, our staff and volunteers and to the many other people that
contribute to an event like this, and as we cannot uphold that duty at the
Sadly, postponement until later this year was not an option either.
